<blockquote cite="#comment-169579"><p>Attempting to discuss things with you in a manner that you do not permit (i.e. using humor rather than exceeding academic verbosity) is tiresome, grating, and in all honesty makes me unsure of what you hope to accomplish insofar as having an open dialogue with people who are not exactly like-minded as you.</p></blockquote>
